title: Summoner level not updated
body:
I have been level 30 for awhile, but when i sign into the boards it shows I'm still level 5. 

Can this be updated so I can participate in the boards?

replies.body: An account sometimes has to sync to the boards when posting for the first time.  It looks like your'e now appearing as level 30!  Let me know if you still have any issues posting!
